# Installation Guide For PixelPlusUI on Realme Realme 6/6i/6S (RMX2001 / RMX2002 / RMX2003)

### CLEAN FLASH (RECOMMENDED) : 
1. Download the latest build
2. Reboot to recovery.
3. Take a backup.
4. Wipe System, Data, Cache, Dalvik, Vendor [Only when you are decrypted else you have to format data in recovery]
5. Flash the latest build
6. Flash Magisk [OPTIONAL]
7. Reboot :p

### DIRTY FLASH IF AN UPDATE
1. Download the latest build
2. Reboot to recovery
3. Flash the latest build
4. Flash Magisk [OPTIONAL]
5. Wipe Cache
6. Reboot :p

## Note: 
• Best Firmware for the device is B61, so try to use ROMs on it
• PBRP recommended for flashing
